#Factory Unit 0047
de:
facunit.message1 = The [red]Arumis[] closed operation of [accent]Factory Unit No.0047[]\nThe base hasn't been maintained in decades leaving it to wither away.
facunit.message2 = The factory was left to fend for itself.\nWhatever unit production it has, is their only way to fight back.
facunit.message3 = Asthosus had thousands of factories built and operated by [red]Arumis[].\nOver time it was proven to be very difficult to maintain, some were lost by beasts who shoot white blood.
facunit.message4 = Mass closure began factory by factory, leaving them to be either engulfed by sandstorms,\ncrumble and turn to scrap piles, slowly deteriorate or even be infested.
facunit.message5 = Only functional factory units left are:\n[accent]#0047 - status = [lightgray]closed\n[accent]#0072 - status = [lightgray]unavailable
facunit.message6 = Years ago when factories were active,\n[red]Arumis[] would deliver advanced equipment to ones who couldn't build them themselves.
facunit.message7 = Due to the [red]Arumis[] neglecting this sector,\nthere is nothing stopping you from utilizing [accent]turrets[] to attack the base.
facunit.message8 = [red]Arumis Junkyard [gray]#9344
facunit.message9 = [lightgray]Payload to be recycled: --73--\nPayload to be incinerated: --107--\n\nResource count: 277%
