#Molten Heights
de:
molten.message1 = Research Document #7988\nBarite Creatures are fascinating beings, just like any creature they are also prone to infighting despite living as a hive and sometimes to prove dominance will ally with anything or anyone.
molten.message2 = Research Document #8825\nThere are many ways to tame a wild beast on Asthosus, from offering resources to offering methods to show dominance against their rivals.
molten.message3 = Research Document #9987\nDespite being very cooperative creatures, the very moment their needs and goals are satisfied they ditch the relationship entirely and return to their hives.
